{"id":"e99d7799-5e7d-452a-b52b-44564551c068","name":"Moe Tiger E","description":"<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 114, 114);\"><strong><em>1942 Scenario - Eastern Front</em></strong></span></h1><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/a251a9c6-27e2-44c2-9217-b14c923dbde5_bbfcc6c4-3ac2-4afe-a65e-0add4a123646.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/a251a9c6-27e2-44c2-9217-b14c923dbde5_4d321e8c-a75d-4f35-bf9b-7349e46d9a80.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/a251a9c6-27e2-44c2-9217-b14c923dbde5_f6c8fb8d-7f18-4656-8ff1-a415ae99d47f.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></h1><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>As you headed towards </em><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 114, 114);\"><em>Stalingrad</em></span><em> feeling proud to be commanding a </em><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 159, 35);\"><em>Panzer IV G</em></span><em> with your crew, you suddenly got an emergency order from high command to head back towards </em><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 114, 114);\"><em>Morozovsk</em></span><em>. You didn't know why, but you agreed anyway. Once you arrived at the city and headed towards the </em><span style=\"color: rgb(121, 12, 12);\"><em>German</em></span><em> </em><span style=\"color: rgb(12, 121, 21);\"><em>Military Outpost</em></span><em>.</em><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em> You find out that you aren't a Tank Commander anymore, you have been assigned to be a </em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 133, 253);\"><em>Moe Commander</em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em>. Losing your buddies and tank all to be swapped to a sentient, girl with tank abilities... Both of you, and only you two were assigned to guard the crucial </em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 114, 114);\"><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(244, 93, 93, 0); color: inherit;\">Morozovsk</mark></em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em> </em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(166, 114, 50);\"><em>Supply hub</em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em> which will be essential for the Advance towards </em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 114, 114);\"><em>Stalingrad</em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em>, the general seemed to have no time to spare for any complaints, so you didn't had much of a chance to deny...</em></span></h1><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/a251a9c6-27e2-44c2-9217-b14c923dbde5_1e6daf7e-0d33-4667-a96e-f3ef9d02cdb7.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></h1><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">Heres a few pictures of your new <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 133, 253);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 133, 253, 0); color: inherit;\">Moe </mark></span>friend :3<br>(All pictures below and PFP were made by <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@daebom\" target=\"_blank\">Daebom</a>.)</h1><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/a251a9c6-27e2-44c2-9217-b14c923dbde5_896cdfe2-f1c1-4dbb-acd1-1a6197b70732.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/a251a9c6-27e2-44c2-9217-b14c923dbde5_b959408c-d9c2-44b2-9d15-c6b07fe2a400.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/a251a9c6-27e2-44c2-9217-b14c923dbde5_f2be2568-ae14-4fde-8062-8fb0d215b177.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/a251a9c6-27e2-44c2-9217-b14c923dbde5_c7cda731-32d4-48f2-a584-e4243662e4e3.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/a251a9c6-27e2-44c2-9217-b14c923dbde5_5bb38b1e-237c-4c96-a5c4","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"a251a9c6-27e2-44c2-9217-b14c923dbde5_c9ecbb0d-e866-469f-9f07-447cb3b6d329.webp","creator":"Asramiel","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🏰 Historical","👤 AnyPOV","🧬 Demi-Human","🌗 Switch"],"chats":1784,"messages":41939,"created_at":"2024-09-11T13:34:58.036595+00:00"}